name: CracowAir
0:
”Alexa, ask Cracow Air to tell me if there is smog”
”Alexa, is there smog in Cracow Air?”
”Alexa, ask Cracow Air is there smog?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cracow air
des: Tells if there is smog in the air in Cracow in Poland. Provides descriptive information based on Air Quality Index and exact PM 10 value recently measured in Cracow on Dietla 84 street.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
